<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 4 (Marta) - Start</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エミル</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Emil</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>マルタ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Marta</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うーん。　どうしよう……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hmmm. What should I do...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エ〜ミル♪
難しい顔して、どうしたの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>E〜mil♪.
Why do you look so serious?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あ、うん。
けっこう前からなんだけど
シェリアさんが手紙を送ってきてくれるんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh, right. She's been doing it for a while now,
but Cheria-san's been sending me letters.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>一度来てください、話がしたいって。
そんな内容のが何通も</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>"Please come over sometime, I'd like to talk
with you", she says. She's sent a bunch like that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>えぇぇぇぇぇ！！？
そ、それってラブレター！！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whaaaaat?!!
A-Are those love letters?!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>え？　ちが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? No, they're...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>許せない！
エミルは私だけの王子様なのに！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Unforgiveable!
Emil is MY prince, and only mine!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>すぐに文句言ってこなきゃ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I have to go make my complaint right away!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あっ、ま、待ってよ、マルタ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah, h-hold on, Marta!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
